:: right_hand_mm_right_hand_ml_1
<<nobr>>
<<speech "thalara">>You return to me as though retracing your own footsteps. Do you think the ground will feel the same beneath them?<</speech>><br>

<<speech "mc">>I need it back. The grip, the strength, the callus. I don‚Äôt want this softness in me anymore.<</speech>><br>

